    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, a definitive example of BMW\u2019s naturally aspirated zenith. This specimen is powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure dual-VANOS system for optimized cam phasing. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis has undergone preventative subframe reinforcement, and the rod bearing service is fully documented to ensure long-term reliability. The suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings and original-spec dampers. Finished in concours-level paint with a cabin free of typical bolster wear or trim delamination, this vehicle represents a turnkey opportunity for the discerning purist.",
